{"vv30:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv30:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv30:0.3":"Paricchattakavagga ","vv30:0.4":"2. Ucchudayikavimanavatthu ","vv30:1.1":"“Obhasayitva pathavim sadevakam, ","vv30:1.2":"Atirocasi candimasuriya viya; ","vv30:1.3":"Siriya ca vannena yasena tejasa, ","vv30:1.4":"Brahmava deve tidase sahindake. ","vv30:2.1":"Pucchami tam uppalamaladharini, ","vv30:2.2":"Avelini kancanasannibhattace; ","vv30:2.3":"Alankate uttamavatthadharini, ","vv30:2.4":"Ka tvam subhe devate vandase mamam. ","vv30:3.1":"Kim tvam pure kammamakasi attana, ","vv30:3.2":"Manussabhuta purimaya jatiya; ","vv30:3.3":"Danam sucinnam atha silasamyamam, ","vv30:3.4":"Kenupapanna sugatim yasassini; ","vv30:3.5":"Devate pucchitacikkha, ","vv30:3.6":"Kissa kammassidam phalan”ti. ","vv30:4.1":"“Idani bhante imameva gamam, ","vv30:4.2":"Pindaya amhakam gharam upagami; ","vv30:4.3":"Tato te ucchussa adasi khandikam, ","vv30:4.4":"Pasannacitta atulaya pitiya. ","vv30:5.1":"Sassu ca paccha anuyunjate mamam, ","vv30:5.2":"Kaham nu ucchum vadhuke avakiri; ","vv30:5.3":"Na chadditam no pana khaditam maya, ","vv30:5.4":"Santassa bhikkhussa sayam adasaham. ","vv30:6.1":"Tuyham nvidam issariyam atho mama, ","vv30:6.2":"Itissa sassu paribhasate mamam; ","vv30:6.3":"Pitham gahetva paharam adasi me, ","vv30:6.4":"Tato cuta kalakatamhi devata. ","vv30:7.1":"Tadeva kammam kusalam katam maya, ","vv30:7.2":"Sukhanca kammam anubhomi attana; ","vv30:7.3":"Devehi saddhim paricarayamaham, ","vv30:7.4":"Modamaham kamagunehi pancahi. ","vv30:8.1":"Tadeva kammam kusalam katam maya, ","vv30:8.2":"Sukhanca kammam anubhomi attana; ","vv30:8.3":"Devindagutta tidasehi rakkhita, ","vv30:8.4":"Samappita kamagunehi pancahi. ","vv30:9.1":"Etadisam punnaphalam anappakam, ","vv30:9.2":"Mahavipaka mama ucchudakkhina; ","vv30:9.3":"Devehi saddhim paricarayamaham, ","vv30:9.4":"Modamaham kamagunehi pancahi. ","vv30:10.1":"Etadisam punnaphalam anappakam, ","vv30:10.2":"Mahajutika mama ucchudakkhina; ","vv30:10.3":"Devindagutta tidasehi rakkhita, ","vv30:10.4":"Sahassanettoriva nandane vane. ","vv30:11.1":"Tuvanca bhante anukampakam vidum, ","vv30:11.2":"Upecca vandim kusalanca pucchisam; ","vv30:11.3":"Tato te ucchussa adasi khandikam, ","vv30:11.4":"Pasannacitta atulaya pitiya”ti. ","vv30:12.1":"Ucchudayikavimanam dutiyam. "}